      "code-smell-detection": "Watch for these anti-patterns:\n### 1. Long Functions\n### 2. Deep Nesting\n### 3. Magic Numbers\n**Remember**: Code quality is not negotiable. Clear, maintainable code enables rapid development and confident refactoring."
